    "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/tarball/2.3.2",
    "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/zipball/2.3.2",
    "body": "## Notes:\r\n- Since version 26.2+, Mojang has introduced the Vulkan rendering engine. If your device does **not** support **Vulkan 1.2**, you **may** be unable to launch the latest version of Minecraft.\r\n\r\n## Updates:\r\n- Synced translations from [Weblate project](https://hosted.weblate.org/projects/zalithlauncher2/)\r\n- Added Thai language option to the language list by [youfeng11](https://github.com/youfeng11)\r\n- Added support for rendering with SurfaceView\r\n\r\n## Changes:\r\n- Accounts: Refresh Microsoft account only when the token expires\r\n\r\n## Fixes:\r\n- Input method:\r\n  - Crashes related to focus issues\r\n  - Enter key not responding properly in the input method",
